# ENTITY::SET_CAN_AUTO_VAULT_ON_ENTITY

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity
* **BOOL** canAutoVault

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Prevent auto vaulting on a particular entity.

p1 always false.
